              h5 Collection of Personal Information
              p You may choose to give us personal information directly in a variety of situations. For example, you may want to give us your name and contact information to communicate with you, to inquire about an order, to provide you with a subscription or a service, or to do business with us if you are a supplier or a business partner. If you tell us that you do not want us to use your information to make further contact with you beyond fulfilling your request, we will respect your wishes.
